{
  "formatVersion": "1.0.0",
  "title": "Install fiji-mcp",
  "rounds": [
    {
      "id": "r-clone",
      "kind": "terminal",
      "prompt": "git clone https://github.com/SteffenPL/fiji-mcp.git && cd fiji-mcp",
      "included": true,
      "steps": [
        {
          "id": "s-clone-1",
          "included": true,
          "displayMode": "normal",
          "inserted": {
            "type": "status",
            "text": "fiji-mcp repository cloned",
            "variant": "success",
            "comment": {
              "en": "Source repository: <a href=\"https://github.com/SteffenPL/fiji-mcp\">SteffenPL/fiji-mcp</a>. The tutorial uses <a href=\"https://docs.astral.sh/uv/\">uv</a> for the Python environment.",
              "ja": "ソースリポジトリ: <a href=\"https://github.com/SteffenPL/fiji-mcp\">SteffenPL/fiji-mcp</a>。このチュートリアルでは Python 環境に <a href=\"https://docs.astral.sh/uv/\">uv</a> を使います。"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ins-1001",
      "kind": "terminal",
      "prompt": "uv sync",
      "steps": [
        {
          "id": "ins-1002",
          "included": true,
          "displayMode": "normal",
          "inserted": {
            "type": "status",
            "text": "Python environment ready",
            "variant": "success"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "r-install",
      "kind": "terminal",
      "prompt": "uv run fiji-mcp install",
      "included": true,
      "steps": [
        {
          "id": "s-install-1",
          "included": true,
          "displayMode": "normal",
          "inserted": {
            "type": "output",
            "text": "Fiji found at /Applications/Fiji.app\nBridge plugin copied to Fiji plugins/\nFiji path saved to .fiji-path",
            "comment": {
              "en": "This installs the Fiji-side bridge plugin. If Fiji is not in a standard location, run <code>uv run fiji-mcp install --fiji-home /path/to/Fiji.app</code>.",
              "ja": "Fiji 側のブリッジプラグインをインストールします。Fiji が標準の場所にない場合は <code>uv run fiji-mcp install --fiji-home /path/to/Fiji.app</code> を使います。"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "s-install-2",
          "included": true,
          "displayMode": "normal",
          "inserted": {
            "type": "status",
            "text": "bridge plugin installed into Fiji",
            "variant": "success"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "r-mcp-add",
      "kind": "terminal",
      "prompt": "claude mcp add --scope project fiji-mcp -- uv run --directory /Users/steffen/fiji-mcp fiji-mcp",
      "included": true,
      "steps": [
        {
          "id": "s-mcp-add-1",
          "included": true,
          "displayMode": "normal",
          "inserted": {
            "type": "output",
            "text": "Added fiji-mcp to project MCP config (.mcp.json)",
            "comment": {
              "en": "Register the server with Claude Code. The <code>--directory</code> value should be the absolute path to your fiji-mcp clone.",
              "ja": "Claude Code に MCP サーバーを登録します。<code>--directory</code> には fiji-mcp クローンへの絶対パスを指定します。"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "s-mcp-add-2",
          "included": true,
          "displayMode": "normal",
          "inserted": {
            "type": "status",
            "text": "MCP server registered",
            "variant": "success"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "r-open-image",
      "kind": "claude",
      "prompt": "Open the ImageJ sample image blobs.gif in Fiji using the run_ij_macro tool with this macro code: open(\"https://imagej.net/images/blobs.gif\");",
      "included": true,
      "steps": [
        {
          "id": "s-open-fiji-main",
          "included": true,
          "displayMode": "normal",
          "inserted": {
            "type": "window",
            "windowTitle": "(Fiji Is Just) ImageJ",
            "content": {
              "kind": "fiji-main"
            },
            "comment": {
              "en": "With fiji-mcp registered, Claude Code can launch Fiji and connect the bridge plugin automatically.",
              "ja": "fiji-mcp を登録すると、Claude Code が Fiji を起動し、ブリッジプラグインへ自動接続できます。"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "s-open-1",
          "included": false,
          "displayMode": "compact",
          "inserted": {
            "type": "thinking",
            "text": "The user wants to open the ImageJ sample image blobs.gif in Fiji using the run_ij_macro tool. Let me use the fiji-mcp skill/tool to do this."
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "s-open-2",
          "included": false,
          "displayMode": "compact",
          "inserted": {
            "type": "assistant",
            "html": "<p>I'll open the blobs.gif image in Fiji using the run_ij_macro tool now.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "s-open-3",
          "included": true,
          "displayMode": "normal",
          "inserted": {
            "type": "tool_call",
            "toolName": "fiji-mcp · run_ij_macro",
            "code": "open(\"https://imagej.net/images/blobs.gif\");",
            "comment": {
              "en": "Claude runs a short ImageJ macro through the MCP tool.",
              "ja": "Claude が MCP ツール経由で短い ImageJ マクロを実行します。"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "s-open-4",
          "included": false,
          "displayMode": "compact",
          "inserted": {
            "type": "tool_result",
            "text": "{\"status\":\"completed\",\"stdout\":\"\",\"stderr\":\"\",\"value\":null,\"error\":null,\"duration_ms\":1595,\"active_image\":\"blobs.gif\",\"dismissed_dialogs\":[],\"results_snapshot\":null}"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "s-open-5",
          "included": true,
          "displayMode": "normal",
          "inserted": {
            "type": "assistant",
            "html": "<p>The image <code>blobs.gif</code> opened successfully in Fiji — the active image is now <code>blobs.gif</code>.</p>",
            "final": true
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "r-thumbnail",
      "kind": "claude",
      "prompt": "Now get a thumbnail of the opened blobs.gif image using the get_thumbnail tool.",
      "included": true,
      "steps": [
        {
          "id": "s-thumb-1",
          "included": false,
          "displayMode": "compact",
          "inserted": {
            "type": "thinking",
            "text": "The user wants to get a thumbnail of the blobs.gif image using the get_thumbnail tool."
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "s-thumb-2",
          "included": true,
          "displayMode": "normal",
          "inserted": {
            "type": "tool_call",
            "toolName": "fiji-mcp · get_thumbnail",
            "code": "title: blobs.gif"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "s-thumb-3",
          "included": false,
          "displayMode": "compact",
          "inserted": {
            "type": "tool_result",
            "text": "{\"path\":\"/var/folders/.../fiji_mcp_thumb_1777022999174.png\",\"width\":256,\"height\":254,\"is_inverted\":true}"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "s-thumb-4",
          "included": true,
          "displayMode": "normal",
          "inserted": {
            "type": "window",
            "windowTitle": "blobs.gif",
            "subtitle": "256×254 · 8-bit · inverted LUT",
            "content": {
              "kind": "fiji-image",
              "src": "blobs_thumbnail.png",
              "statusBar": "256×254 pixels; 8-bit; inverted LUT"
            },
            "comment": {
              "en": "The thumbnail gives Claude visual feedback from Fiji, including the current LUT and display range.",
              "ja": "サムネイルにより、現在の LUT や表示範囲を含めた Fiji の見た目を Claude が確認できます。"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "s-thumb-5",
          "included": true,
          "displayMode": "normal",
          "inserted": {
            "type": "assistant",
            "html": "<p>Here's the thumbnail of <code>blobs.gif</code> — 256×254 pixels, showing the classic dark circular blobs on a bright background.</p>",
            "final": true,
            "comment": {
              "en": "That is the basic loop: install the bridge, register it as MCP, run a macro, and inspect the image result.",
              "ja": "基本の流れはこれで完了です。ブリッジをインストールし、MCP として登録し、マクロを実行して画像結果を確認します。"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
